<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Rihanna's Amazon documentary will be released 'around' US Independence Day which is July 4.</p>

<p>The documentary is being directed by Hollywood filmmaker Peter Berg, who revealed that shooting the film has been an 'epic journey' over a four-year period.</p>

<p>'The Rihanna doc is something I've been working on with her for almost four years now,' he said. 'Amazon's gonna release it summer next year, sometime hopefully around the fourth of July. It's been a really epic journey, the past four years with her.'</p>

